{"source_url": "https://www.boomlive.in/news/as-geopolitical-tensions-rise-rbi-trims-growth-raises-inflation-estimates-17466", "article_heading": "As Geopolitical Tensions Rise, RBI Trims Growth, Raises Inflation Estimates", "short_context": "Growth forecasts has been cut to 7.2% from 7.8%, while inflation outlook has been raised to 5.7% from 4.5%", "short_into": "The Reserve Bank of India (RBI) on Friday raised its outlook on inflation and cut growth estimates, due to geopolitical tensions. This statement made by RBI Governor Shakitkanta Das was his first bi-monthly monetary policy address since the onset of the military conflict between Russia and Ukraine on February 24, and his statement shows that it has played a role in determining India's monetary policy outlook. ", "author": "Mohammed Kudrati", "date": "8 April 2022 7:54 AM GMT", "image_set1": ["https://www.boomlive.in/h-upload/2021/02/05/940792-rbi-feb-governor-das.webp"], "image_set2": []}
